name: "What's in the package?"
description: It was a beautiful day, until someone chasing at my package delivery. I need to secure this thing! The Hunter still chasing me. There's a police, but I think he doesn't response me. Then I heard someone get hit. There's a girl with a skull mask, she helped me. *click* A gun? Why is he pointing the gun at me! What happened? What is actually this package?!
